## 4. Key Modules (Based on Codebase)
| Module | Description |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Auth** | Login, Signup, OTP, Google Auth, Password Reset. |
| **Shop** | Product listing, Categories, Filtering, Search. |
| **Order** | Cart management, Checkout process, Order tracking. |
| **Seller** | Vendor registration, Profile management, Product upload. |
| **Content** | Blogs, Videos, Hero Banners (Carousel). |
| **Location** | City and Pincode specific service fees. |

## 5. Current State & Observations
*   **Server Robustness:** The server is configured to attempt startup even if the Database connection fails (fallback mode).
*   **Data Integrity:** The "Backup to JSON" strategy for orders is unique and ensures you have a file-based record of sales even if the DB is inaccessible.
